name: Kapan take-profit?
description:
Featuring a scene from the One Piece series episode 872, where Luffy fights Katakuri.

This gif is a screenshot of Luffy saying "I'm the one who decides my own future!", with the additional caption "when it's time to take-profit" so it's as if Luffy is saying "I'm the one who decides when it's time to take-profit!"

Additional subtitles and captions that appear are written in Indonesian.
